Package: work.tkgstrator.kiouusiproxy
Name: KiouUsiProxy
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: KIOU (Shogi) USI bridge tweak. Observes the in-game board state (SFEN) and committed moves (USI) and exposes them over a local gRPC endpoint so a host-side proxy can drive a desktop USI engine (YaneuraOu et al.) against the live position. Read-only with respect to game state — no items, currency, or server messages are modified. Companion tweak to KiouEditor; they can be installed together. For authorized testing only.
Maintainer: NEVER KNOWS BEST
Author: tkgstrator
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate
